<note n="0671006" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0671006">二十三＝十八【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0671009" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0671009">（不）＋自【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
